 
 
 

GENDER PAY GAP REPORT - 2017 

 

 

 

 
Under  the  Equality  Act  2010  (Gender  Pay  Gap  Information)  Regulations  2017,  any  UK  organisation 
employing more than 250 employees has to report its gender pay gap.  The report comprises six different 
metrics and a narrative to explain the organisation’s gender pay gap position:  
 

 
 
 
 
